channel.title: I need help with my server
channel.description:
I am trying to make my own server and im looking through different sources to find the best one. I have found one but i can't figure out why i cant portforward. I am currently trying to use hamachi. If someone can help me and try out my server on hamachi post on this and i will check it so i can keep the server source running.
Server ip: thrillscapev2.no-ip.biz password: 123
